posting_body: ['Text', 'show contact info', '0 to setup a showing!', 'AREA: Parker', 'FEATURES:', 'Two story single family home with vaulted ceilings, fireplace, sprinkler system and additional storage!', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED:', 'Electric stove, refrigerator with ice maker, dishwasher, microwave, and garbage disposal.', 'LAUNDRY: Laundry room with washer/dryer hookups only.', 'FLOORING: Carpet/vinyl/tile flooring.', 'HEAT/COOLING: Gas heat and central A/C.', 'PARKING: Two car garage', 'FENCING: Fully fenced yard!', 'BASEMENT: unfinished basement', 'PETS: Pets considered with a one-time non-refundable pet fee of $250 per pet.', 'Sorry', 'but we cannot allow any of the following breeds of dog: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, and Staffordshire Bull Terrier.', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT:', "Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult.', 'AVAILABILITY DATE: August 6th!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 1 week of the property's listed availability date.", '**', 'LEASE TERM:  Initial lease to end April through June of 2023 with 12-month extensions possible at that time.', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
